Tested on Ubuntu 10.04 lucid and Debian squeeze only.

build-essential python git-core autoconf scons

debian build:
  debhelper libfltk1.1-dev libhamlib-dev libjpeg62-dev libxft-dev
  libpng-dev zlib1g-dev libexpat-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile-dev
  libsamplerate-dev libcurl4-openssl-dev | libcurl4-gnutls-dev libpulse-dev
  libxmlrpc-c3-dev cdbs quilt libssl-dev libpulse-dev devscripts

windows build:
  gcc-mingw32 nsis unzip
